# Blog Taxonomy Archive (naghoos)

Separate from [`templates/blog.php`](templates/blog.php) (ACF landing page with tabs).

## Template hierarchy

| URL | Template |
|-----|----------|
| `/category/{slug}/` | `category.php` |
| `/tag/{slug}/` | `tag.php` |
| Other archives | `archive.php` (fallback) |

All route to [`partials/parts/blog/archive-layout.php`](partials/parts/blog/archive-layout.php).

## Layout grid

`lg:grid-cols-13` — sidebar `lg:col-span-4 xl:col-span-3`, content `lg:col-span-9 xl:col-span-10`.

## Partials

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `archive-layout.php` | Query, grid, loop, term description |
| `archive-toolbar.php` | Title + sort pills (xl+) + mobile sort select + filter button |
| `archive-sidebar.php` | Hierarchical categories + tags (accordion) |
| `archive-mobile-filter.php` | Modal `blog-filter-modal` with sidebar duplicate |
| `pagination.php` | `mode: archive` — `get_pagenum_link()` + preserves `orderby` |

## Query (`archive-layout.php`)

- `posts_per_page: 24`
- Sort via `?orderby=`:

| Value | Query |
|-------|--------|
| (empty) / `date` | `date DESC` |
| `date-asc` | `date ASC` |
| `popularity` | `meta_key: post_views_count`, `meta_value_num DESC` |

## Sidebar

- Direct `get_term_link()` navigation (no cross-tax filters)
- Active: `bg-cynRed text-white`
- Nested category accordion; `sidebar_suffix` for mobile modal IDs

## JS

- `accordion.js` — sidebar accordions
- `modals.js` — mobile filter modal
- `blogArchiveSort.js` — mobile sort `<select data-blog-archive-sort>`

## Cards

`Templates::getCard('blog', ['layout' => 'horizontal', 'responsive' => true, 'fixed' => true])`
